Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食組合將會解散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們日食將變回普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散演唱會將會在蔚藍王國舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭 皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要來啊 這是日食最後的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖也很想見到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等待傳說的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在叫你了 傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這是怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食沒有回月亮上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就在粉絲中流傳著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖的病情已經嚴重到無法返回月球的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只不過是傳言罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這和傳說也有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 丹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是丹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很彆扭 胸口附近 無法釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 就是平靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人 UNDERGROUND 渦輪城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股煩躁到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡…好疼…冷靜點 笨蛋丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生也一定感覺到了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有成長一點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是帶著煩惱長大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很嚴密的戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝羅納迪克公司的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在誰都無法奪走CANNON了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒多少時間了 馬上就是最後的聆聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 石頭有傾訴什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計畫順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日食的歌聲活化阿魯迪紐姆礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能再次聽到石頭的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 王通過這最後的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了引導國家之後千年的繁榮所必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民也一定會傳頌王的偉大功績的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍王國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拯救月亮和阿斯達修的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免這兩顆行星的衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓您看到傳說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩兩天了 能趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能趕上的 楊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是日食最後的演唱會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們看看所謂的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣好嗎 都沒怎麼彩排過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是她們的彩排了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮歐蕾特 為了傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救月亮和阿斯達修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以露玖才要求改造升級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為真正的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 子彈號和你的ZEPHYR都還不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備完成後我們也會跟上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能趕上 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊打算把日食怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不清楚他的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是照預定計畫準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用盡時間 盡可能在阿斯達修上找尋傳說候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,評委會看到前段時間的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經作出了接受丹的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼去月球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有辦法奪取MOON CANNON了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是還是有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要追上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真讓人擔心啊 露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲鈍了 阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 見到露玖小姐之後要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想著 見到再說 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到了 心中的煩躁也許就能消散了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖小姐很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想說 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去見露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道女人都在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想只會越煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣說我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.56,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『主翻』willyer『校正』willyer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是趕上明天的演唱會了 芍詹德博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了激活礦石 從而提取傳說子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要的就只有丹．JD了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了宣告傳說的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我的聲音無法傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 誰都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過旅行 看過世界 受過傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲痛之後變強的你的聲音 也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在附近吧 佛蘿拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非要打扮成這副樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了展現你的醜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是搶奪MOON CANNON而被通緝的賞金罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喬裝改扮是無法入國的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做了那點事就要被通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍王國的那些人氣量真小 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹是醜男 少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說怎麼樣…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出示ID
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不被識破 請不要發出大聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丹 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是醜的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰醜了 一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像啊 醜男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生 安靜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你是醜男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看仔細了 通緝告示和真正的灌籃假面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灌籃假面…抓住他…是懸賞罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 都是你害我們被識破了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推卸責任 笨蛋丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 戒備更加森嚴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其它地方能進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城的周圍都加強了防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該到處都有守備盯梢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下水道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從山上流到城裡的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是水很急 所以很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了很危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有金蛋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 斯帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨瘦如柴呢 有好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 丹來見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊 露玖的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 她會直接來會場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚日食將成為傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活阿魯迪紐姆礦石 用它的排斥力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把接近的月球推回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合三人之力 拯救月球和阿斯達修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 Basquasher
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquasher？ 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 會感冒的 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不脫掉會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快脫 快脫 都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我還沒有心理準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很熟悉嘛 靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然要繞遠路 在三後街區後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得見嗎 露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演員都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開幕的鈴聲就會響起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見嗎 露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灌籃假面 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他入侵了 快抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生 見到露玖小姐後你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了解開心中的煩悶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手就擒吧 灌籃假面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生 為什麼要Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦呢 Basquash是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Basquash是不會說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有表裡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的力量相互碰撞 彈飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈奏出各種旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著彎曲的道路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是生存方式本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼盡全力生存下去 展現真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爺 醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的旅行結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 現在起新的旅程即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為佛蘿拉．斯凱布魯姆的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看著你Basquash的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…皇族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛蘿拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又扮女裝？ 你很喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為面前的這位是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位可是國王雷伽歷亞13世的第二公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛蘿拉．斯凱布魯姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭抬太高了 都低下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說是女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來是女的啊 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去露玖的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的旅程還要繼續下去 丹．JD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灌籃假面正在被通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭低下去 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救月球和阿斯達修 為了傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了有一天我也能成為真正的Basquasher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時再一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也擔心露玖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我是斯凱布魯姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣 你不也是Basquasher嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Basquasher？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一起去吧
